---------------------------
|          Kodes          |
---------------------------

Kodes is a simple app that is designed to
allow testing of front-end ajax response handlers
against HTTP status codes, to be sure all cases,
error, redirects etc, are treated and rendered
correctly.

= INSTALLATION =

Download, clone, copy/paste are all methods you
can use.

git clone git@github.com:ekynoxe/kodes.git


= RUNNING =

* Make sure you've got sinatra installed:

	gem install sinatra

* Run!

	ruby kodes.rb


